list.abstract: REACH（英[riːtʃ]，美[riːtʃ]），英语单词，作动词为伸臂够、到达、达到等。作名词为伸出、地带、大片地区等。短语搭配为reach out（伸出援手）。例句有I wanted to reach businesses too.（我也想到企业去）。 REACH的不及物动词近义词有go、range、arrive at。名词近义词有extent、boundary等；不及物动词的近义词有accomplish、affect等。arrive指得出结论，达成某项协议或作出某一决定等。reach，指到达某一空间、时间、目标或发展过程中的某一点。
《REACH》是由Estefan、Warren作词、作曲，Gloria Estefan演唱的歌曲，该歌曲收录于2001年2月1日发行的《Gloria Estefan-Greatest Hits Vol.2》专辑中。这首歌也是1996年亚特兰大奥运会的主题歌。

yingyinNormal.en: In a traditional steel mill, furnaces are powered by burning fuel and can take days to reach the right temperature.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在传统的钢铁公司熔炉，由动力燃料燃烧驱动，一天之内就能达到正温。

yingyinNormal.en: But the problem is economies can take a long time to reach their equilibrium and may even stall along the way. And in the meantime people can get a little frustrated.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但问题是经济得需要很多时间才能达到出入平衡，而且还有可能什么进展都没有。所以在这时，人们对这样的作法可能会有点失望。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah. If you can reach 'em.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但你无法去找他们。

yingyinNormal.en: Then when you reach the mainland...
yingyinNormal.zh: 接着你到了大陆...

yingyinNormal.en: If Luke couldn't reach him, how could I?
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果卢克都找不到他，我怎么可能做到？

yingyinNormal.en: You will reach your destination in 100 yards.
yingyinNormal.zh: 距离你的目的地还有100码。

yingyinNormal.en: The dwarves were never meant to reach Erebor.
yingyinNormal.zh: 它根本不想让这群矮人抵达埃瑞博。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《The Hobbit: The Battle of the Five Armies》

yingyinNormal.en: You will reach your destination in 300 yards.
yingyinNormal.zh: 距离你的目的地还有300码。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, dear. Daddy Pig cannot reach his pancake.
yingyinNormal.zh: 噢，天哪。猪爸爸够不到他的煎饼了。

yingyinNormal.en: I fear Ariq's horses will never reach Xiangyang.
yingyinNormal.zh: 恐怕阿里不哥的人马永远到不了襄阳。

yingyinNormal.en: I've contacted the Kremlin. They said he'll reach out soon.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我联系了克里姆林宫，对方说稍后回话。

yingyinNormal.en: To reach the terminal, you'll need to pass the main gates.
yingyinNormal.zh: 要抵达这个终端计算机，你需要通过几扇设施大门。

yingyinNormal.en: The judge is having us sequestered until we reach a verdict.
yingyinNormal.zh: 法官要求我们做出一致裁决前必须与世隔绝。

yingyinNormal.en: And if I wanted something, I could just reach out and take it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果我想要什么就伸手去拿。

yingyinNormal.en: The vote isn't until tomorrow afternoon. I'll reach out to Mendoza.
yingyinNormal.zh: 明天下午才开始投票，我一早就会联系Mendoza。

yingyinNormal.en: I've already talked to your parents, at least, those I could reach.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我已经跟你们父母谈过了，至少是我能联系的到的。

yingyinNormal.en: You need any help? Uh, yeah, can you reach that gravy boat up there?
yingyinNormal.zh: 要帮忙吗？嗯，你能不能拿到上面那个调味壶？

yingyinNormal.en: Let's reach out and see if Detective Riley has happened by any of them.
yingyinNormal.zh: 咱查查看莱利警探是不是露过面了。

yingyinNormal.en: The rebels will reach the outskirts of the Capitol in a matter of days.
yingyinNormal.zh: 几天后，叛军就将抵达国会区外围。

yingyinNormal.en: How about on the roof? What's the matter, Potter? Bit beyond your reach?
yingyinNormal.zh: 屋顶上怎么样？怎么啦，波特，是不是够不着啦？

数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: Unless a broad consensus can be <highlight>reached</highlight> on reforming the international tax system, other nations are likely to follow suit.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 除非就改革国际税收体系达成广泛共识，否则其他国家很可能会效仿。

examination_example.sentence: That conflicted with how I needed to train to <highlight>reach</highlight> my goals.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这与我需要如何训练才能达到目标相冲突。

examination_example.sentence: Emerging in the late Sixties and <highlight>reaching</highlight> a peak in the Seventies, Land Art was one of a range of new forms.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 地景艺术在六十年代末兴起，在七十年代达到高峰，是一系列新形式中的一种。

examination_example.sentence: The priorities and expectations defined by the young will <highlight>reach</highlight> almost all aspects of American life.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 年轻人所确定的优先事项和期望几乎会影响到美国生活的各个方面。

examination_example.sentence: The case may yet <highlight>reach</highlight> the Supreme Court.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 此案可能会提交至最高法院。

sense_info_list.en: the limit to which sb/sth has the power or influence to do sth

examination_example.sentence: The <highlight>reach</highlight> of art-science tie-ups needs to go beyond the necessary purpose of research communication, and participants.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 艺术与科学的合作需要超越研究交流的必要目的，甚至是参与者本身。

examination_example.sentence: The request has raised the prospect of regulators wading into early-stage tech markets that until now have been beyond their <highlight>reach</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这一要求增加了监管机构涉足早期科技市场的可能性，而迄今为止，监管机构还无法涉足这些市场。

examination_example.sentence_trans: 艺术家帮助科学家接触到更广泛的受众，并与之建立情感联系，促进学习。

within one's reach 在某人可及范围内

word_usage.usage:
reach表“到达”某地时，为瞬间及物动词，不与表示一段时间或状态的状语连用。
示例：她到公司两个小时了。
误 She reached to the company for two hours.
正 She reached the company two hours ago.

reach作不及物动词时，常与after, for, into等介词连用。
示例：Judy reached into her handbag.
朱蒂把手伸进提包。

examination_example.sentence: Our task is to help students <highlight>reach</highlight> their goals through mentoring.

examination_example.sentence: You should keep matches and lighters out of their <highlight>reach</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 你应该把火柴和打火机放在他们够不着的地方。

word_usage.usage:
reach表“到达”某地时，为瞬间及物动词，不与表示一段时间或状态的状语连用。
示例：她到公司两个小时了。
误 She reached to the company for two hours.
正 She reached the company two hours ago.

reach作不及物动词时，常与after, for, into等介词连用。
示例：Judy reached into her handbag.
朱蒂把手伸进提包。

disambiguation_list.sense_disambiguation: 是不及物动词，其后若跟地点名词时，要在arrive后加介词in或at。arrive in后跟相对较大的地点（如国家或城市），arrive at后跟相对较小的地点（如车站或邮局等）。
是不及物动词，其后跟地点名词，要用get to
是及物动词，其后可以直接跟地点名词，如：reach Beijing 抵达北京。
